    {
      "cell_type": "markdown",

        "id": "575aab7e-8f07-4cf4-8796-4c54cbe361f2"
      },
      "source": [

      ]
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "execution_count": null,
      "id": "eb3ea2c2-4a8a-4269-90ba-6833a8448c82",
      "metadata": {
        "id": "eb3ea2c2-4a8a-4269-90ba-6833a8448c82"
      },
      "outputs": [],
      "source": [
        "# Setup\n",
        "\n",
        "!pip install langchain\n",

    {
      "cell_type": "markdown",
      "id": "64bd25f2-7352-4fee-8288-e2148bbf164a",
      "metadata": {
        "id": "64bd25f2-7352-4fee-8288-e2148bbf164a"
      },
      "source": [
        "# Tools in LangChain"
      ]
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "markdown",
      "id": "27671aea-9e7c-4a4d-9277-5ec86477fb2e",
      "metadata": {
        "id": "27671aea-9e7c-4a4d-9277-5ec86477fb2e"
      },
      "source": [
        "## User-defined Tools"
      ]
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "execution_count": null,
      "id": "b861244c-8e01-43d3-b266-744aa8c203a3",
      "metadata": {
        "id": "b861244c-8e01-43d3-b266-744aa8c203a3"
      },
      "outputs": [],
      "source": [
        "from langchain_core.tools import tool"
      ]
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "execution_count": null,
      "id": "a2d7d36c-5b33-4519-aa84-870e03ed76bb",
      "metadata": {
        "id": "a2d7d36c-5b33-4519-aa84-870e03ed76bb"
      },
      "outputs": [],
      "source": [
        "# built your first tool with @tool decorator\n",
        "\n",
        "@tool\n",
        "def add_tool(a:int, b:int)->int:\n",
        "    '''Sum of two numbers'''\n",
        "    return a+b"
      ]
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "execution_count": null,
      "id": "c2c49e52-49c5-4e43-af32-c67c64ee2c64",
      "metadata": {
        "id": "c2c49e52-49c5-4e43-af32-c67c64ee2c64"
      },
      "outputs": [],
      "source": [
        "print(add_tool.name)\n",
        "print(add_tool.description)\n",
        "print(add_tool.args)"
      ]
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "execution_count": null,
      "id": "8dd59914-2745-4bdd-bf3d-ad3b48bc2992",
      "metadata": {
        "id": "8dd59914-2745-4bdd-bf3d-ad3b48bc2992"
      },
      "outputs": [],
      "source": [
        "# async tool\n",
        "@tool\n",
        "async def aadd_tool(a:int, b:int)->int:\n",
        "    '''Async function to add two numbers'''\n",
        "    return a+b"
      ]
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "execution_count": null,
      "id": "07d17d45-46d6-4f27-ae06-0de91c52108b",
      "metadata": {
        "id": "07d17d45-46d6-4f27-ae06-0de91c52108b"
      },
      "outputs": [],
      "source": [
        "from typing import Annotated,List\n",
        "@tool\n",
        "def multiply_by_sum_tool(\n",
        "    a: Annotated[int,'A Value'],\n",
        "    b: Annotated[List[int],'List of integer values']\n",
        ")->int:\n",
        "    '''Multiply a by summation of b values'''\n",
        "    return a*sum(b)"
      ]
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "execution_count": null,
      "id": "4e725d31-5738-46b4-ab9e-a7fbfd7499fc",
      "metadata": {
        "id": "4e725d31-5738-46b4-ab9e-a7fbfd7499fc"
      },
      "outputs": [],
      "source": [
        "print(multiply_by_sum_tool.args)"
      ]
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "execution_count": null,
      "id": "f7e6dbaa-b2f3-4aaf-9e07-ab71cac32c75",
      "metadata": {
        "id": "f7e6dbaa-b2f3-4aaf-9e07-ab71cac32c75"
      },
      "outputs": [],
      "source": [
        "a = 3\n",
        "b = [6,5,3,4,2]\n",
        "print(multiply_by_sum_tool.invoke({'a':a, 'b':b}))"
      ]
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "markdown",
      "id": "54a83359-cd49-44f8-8579-9571d899b6b1",
      "metadata": {
        "id": "54a83359-cd49-44f8-8579-9571d899b6b1"
      },
      "source": [
        "## Build Custom Prompt Templates"
      ]
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "execution_count": null,
      "id": "c1c339c2-3006-40ac-869d-cbd5627f28a9",
      "metadata": {
        "id": "c1c339c2-3006-40ac-869d-cbd5627f28a9"
      },
      "outputs": [],
      "source": [
        "from langchain_core.tools import StructuredTool\n",
        "\n",
        "def prompt_maker(template: str, values: List[str]) -> str:\n",
        "    '''Function to build final prompt from template and return list of prompts for each value.'''\n",
        "    prompts = [template.format(value=value) for value in values]\n",
        "    return prompts\n",
        "\n",
        "async def aprompt_maker(template: str, values: List[str]) -> str:\n",
        "    '''Async Function to build final prompt from template and return list of prompts for each value.'''\n",
        "    prompts = [template.format(value=value) for value in values]\n",
        "    return prompts\n",
        "\n",
        "prompt_tool = StructuredTool.from_function(func=prompt_maker, coroutine=aprompt_maker)"
      ]
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "execution_count": null,
      "id": "be4f56df-6819-4822-aa90-c57aae37deb8",
      "metadata": {
        "id": "be4f56df-6819-4822-aa90-c57aae37deb8"
      },
      "outputs": [],
      "source": [
        "template = \"Answer the following question in 100 words: {value}\"\n",
        "values = ['Do goldfish grow?','Can cats swim?', 'Difference between hot and cold coffee?']"
      ]
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "execution_count": null,
      "id": "38bec9cd-9927-4827-9226-b092381b09b9",
      "metadata": {
        "id": "38bec9cd-9927-4827-9226-b092381b09b9"
      },
      "outputs": [],
      "source": [
        "print(prompt_tool.invoke({'template':template,'values':values}))"
      ]
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "execution_count": null,
      "id": "f09616aa-7ad5-4208-a572-f3e8654979eb",
      "metadata": {
        "id": "f09616aa-7ad5-4208-a572-f3e8654979eb"
      },
      "outputs": [],
      "source": [
        "print(await prompt_tool.ainvoke({'template':template,'values':values}))"
      ]
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "markdown",
      "id": "3db4add7-e858-4c99-b873-2eb33d0a09b0",
      "metadata": {
        "id": "3db4add7-e858-4c99-b873-2eb33d0a09b0"
      },
      "source": [
        "## LangChain has this to build custom prompts"
      ]
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "execution_count": null,
      "id": "1aa86eb4-8a0d-4c89-812d-315a9ead3d37",
      "metadata": {
        "id": "1aa86eb4-8a0d-4c89-812d-315a9ead3d37"
      },
      "outputs": [],
      "source": [
        "from langchain_core.prompts import PromptTemplate\n",
        "\n",
        "prompt_template = PromptTemplate.from_template(\"Answer the following question in 100 words: {value}\")\n",
        "\n",
        "prompt = prompt_template.invoke({\"value\": 'Do goldfish grow?'})\n",
        "\n",
        "print(prompt)"
      ]
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "markdown",
      "id": "c67b488f-62e3-4501-b3dc-04ddea152f15",
      "metadata": {
        "id": "c67b488f-62e3-4501-b3dc-04ddea152f15"
      },
      "source": [
        "## Predefined Tools"
      ]
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "execution_count": null,
      "id": "daa96d49-1d10-449c-9b4b-3a544c239df5",
      "metadata": {
        "id": "daa96d49-1d10-449c-9b4b-3a544c239df5"
      },
      "outputs": [],
      "source": [
        "#https://python.langchain.com/docs/integrations/tools/"
      ]
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "markdown",
      "id": "60a6f926-c8fd-4cc5-bfe3-ed21a84b424e",
      "metadata": {
        "id": "60a6f926-c8fd-4cc5-bfe3-ed21a84b424e"
      },
      "source": [
        "### Wikipedia"
      ]
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "execution_count": null,
      "id": "b11590e6-5675-48dd-9c65-7db1e593e6bd",
      "metadata": {
        "id": "b11590e6-5675-48dd-9c65-7db1e593e6bd"
      },
      "outputs": [],
      "source": [
        "#%pip install --upgrade --quiet  wikipedia\n",
        "# %pip install langchain-community"
      ]
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "execution_count": null,
      "id": "1c36f789-9c0e-4a60-9384-d675b1f980c0",
      "metadata": {
        "id": "1c36f789-9c0e-4a60-9384-d675b1f980c0"
      },
      "outputs": [],
      "source": [
        "from langchain_community.tools import WikipediaQueryRun\n",
        "from langchain_community.utilities import WikipediaAPIWrapper"
      ]
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "execution_count": null,
      "id": "448fdeff-b33d-411e-a2d0-b550ff66f7cb",
      "metadata": {
        "id": "448fdeff-b33d-411e-a2d0-b550ff66f7cb"
      },
      "outputs": [],
      "source": [
        "api_wrapper = WikipediaAPIWrapper(top_k_results=5, doc_contain_words_max=50)#doc_contain_chars_max=50"
      ]
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "execution_count": null,
      "id": "e99a55d9-274f-4ec6-bf3b-638e1cd066f9",
      "metadata": {
        "id": "e99a55d9-274f-4ec6-bf3b-638e1cd066f9"
      },
      "outputs": [],
      "source": [
        "wiki_tool = WikipediaQueryRun(api_wrapper=api_wrapper)"
      ]
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "execution_count": null,
      "id": "5b2512d4-b55d-463c-8569-083f5f1ad531",
      "metadata": {
        "id": "5b2512d4-b55d-463c-8569-083f5f1ad531"
      },
      "outputs": [],
      "source": [
        "print(wiki_tool.invoke({'query':'Do goldfish grow?'}))"
      ]
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "markdown",
      "id": "ed44f182-43ac-4d10-8659-f8d97eb54857",
      "metadata": {
        "id": "ed44f182-43ac-4d10-8659-f8d97eb54857"
      },
      "source": [
        "### duckduckgo-search"
      ]
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "execution_count": null,
      "id": "2b6ec981-7e40-4651-ab32-58d80974d9c5",
      "metadata": {
        "id": "2b6ec981-7e40-4651-ab32-58d80974d9c5"
      },
      "outputs": [],
      "source": [
        "#%pip install -qU duckduckgo-search langchain-community\n",
        "# %pip install -U ddgs"
      ]
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "execution_count": null,
      "id": "944aa215-5dc3-4cfc-af43-e7a4a96c7a66",
      "metadata": {
        "id": "944aa215-5dc3-4cfc-af43-e7a4a96c7a66"
      },
      "outputs": [],
      "source": [
        "from langchain_community.tools import DuckDuckGoSearchRun\n",
        "\n",
        "ddgs_tool = DuckDuckGoSearchRun()\n",
        "ddgs_tool.invoke(\"Do goldfish grow?\")"
      ]
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "execution_count": null,
      "id": "7b52c2ba-e4a9-4bd1-96c4-3d257bb03316",
      "metadata": {
        "id": "7b52c2ba-e4a9-4bd1-96c4-3d257bb03316"
      },
      "outputs": [],
      "source": [
        "from langchain_community.tools import DuckDuckGoSearchResults\n",
        "\n",
        "ddgs_tool = DuckDuckGoSearchResults()\n",
        "ddgs_tool.invoke(\"Do goldfish grow?\")"
      ]
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "execution_count": null,
      "id": "39d912d0-f9ec-4899-b09d-6682b974f4d0",
      "metadata": {
        "id": "39d912d0-f9ec-4899-b09d-6682b974f4d0"
      },
      "outputs": [],
      "source": [
        "from langchain_community.tools import DuckDuckGoSearchResults\n",
        "ddgs_tool = DuckDuckGoSearchResults(output_format=\"list\")\n",
        "ddgs_tool.invoke(\"Do goldfish grow?\")"
      ]
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "execution_count": null,
      "id": "ae15f910-cc6b-40c5-ac70-68d2ff6e1018",
      "metadata": {
        "id": "ae15f910-cc6b-40c5-ac70-68d2ff6e1018"
      },
      "outputs": [],
      "source": [
        "from langchain_community.utilities import DuckDuckGoSearchAPIWrapper\n",
        "\n",
        "wrapper = DuckDuckGoSearchAPIWrapper(max_results=2)\n",
        "ddgs_tool = DuckDuckGoSearchResults(api_wrapper=wrapper, output_format=\"list\")\n",
        "ddgs_tool.invoke(\"Do goldfish grow?\")"
      ]
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "markdown",
      "id": "181c6ff8-b887-423a-bf73-e402922a3bca",
      "metadata": {
        "id": "181c6ff8-b887-423a-bf73-e402922a3bca"
      },
      "source": [
        "# LLM Initialization using LangChain"
      ]
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "execution_count": null,
      "id": "33db359a-0809-4a83-8dd9-9811e8438f8d",
      "metadata": {
        "id": "33db359a-0809-4a83-8dd9-9811e8438f8d"
      },
      "outputs": [],
      "source": [
        "tools = [add_tool, prompt_tool, wiki_tool, ddgs_tool]"
      ]
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "execution_count": null,
      "id": "be7ed291-bedf-4977-9908-22757ef7dd21",
      "metadata": {
        "id": "be7ed291-bedf-4977-9908-22757ef7dd21"
      },
      "outputs": [],
      "source": [
        "#tools = [{'title':'add_tool', 'description':add_tool},\n",
        "#         {'title':'prompt_tool', 'description':prompt_tool},\n",
        "#        {'title':'wiki_tool', 'description':wiki_tool},\n",
        "#        {'title':'ddgs_tool', 'description':ddgs_tool}]"
      ]
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "execution_count": null,
      "id": "ce5de2f2-d27b-402e-8fb8-de70ffdf9d66",
      "metadata": {
        "id": "ce5de2f2-d27b-402e-8fb8-de70ffdf9d66"
      },
      "outputs": [],
      "source": [
        "tools"
      ]
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "execution_count": null,
      "id": "5edf1a72-20b3-496d-9234-5479e2d28fbe",
      "metadata": {
        "id": "5edf1a72-20b3-496d-9234-5479e2d28fbe"
      },
      "outputs": [],
      "source": [
        "tools[1].name"
      ]
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "execution_count": null,
      "id": "68aa46ef-f2bd-4636-91fa-a89be97e208e",
      "metadata": {
        "id": "68aa46ef-f2bd-4636-91fa-a89be97e208e"
      },
      "outputs": [],
      "source": [
        "# https://python.langchain.com/docs/integrations/chat/\n",
        "\n",
        "#pip install -U langchain-groq\n",
        "# Get The model API Key\n",
        "#https://console.groq.com/keys"
      ]
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "execution_count": null,
      "id": "0f62a2bd-268f-4fc8-8700-8dc808f0c8b1",
      "metadata": {
        "id": "0f62a2bd-268f-4fc8-8700-8dc808f0c8b1"
      },
      "outputs": [],
      "source": [
        "from langchain.chat_models import init_chat_model\n",
        "api_key = ''\n",
        "llm = init_chat_model(\"qwen/qwen3-32b\", model_provider=\"groq\", api_key=api_key)"
      ]
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "execution_count": null,
      "id": "5f4bd37f-728f-4832-966b-45ba75e455ec",
      "metadata": {
        "id": "5f4bd37f-728f-4832-966b-45ba75e455ec"
      },
      "outputs": [],
      "source": [
        "model = llm.bind_tools(tools)"
      ]
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "execution_count": null,
      "id": "0e732033-ec9a-4c37-a8d5-f6ab8f92acf0",
      "metadata": {
        "id": "0e732033-ec9a-4c37-a8d5-f6ab8f92acf0"
      },
      "outputs": [],
      "source": [
        "#prompt = 'What is 2+3?'\n",
        "prompt = 'What is weather today in Kharagpur?'"
      ]
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "execution_count": null,
      "id": "21d59b6d-f53e-4b71-9ce5-a28c055b1373",
      "metadata": {
        "id": "21d59b6d-f53e-4b71-9ce5-a28c055b1373"
      },
      "outputs": [],
      "source": [
        "from langchain_core.messages import HumanMessage\n",
        "messages = [HumanMessage(prompt)]"
      ]
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "execution_count": null,
      "id": "22376948-c08a-4296-b304-6bd23660d05b",
      "metadata": {
        "id": "22376948-c08a-4296-b304-6bd23660d05b"
      },
      "outputs": [],
      "source": [
        "response = model.invoke(messages)"
      ]
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "execution_count": null,
      "id": "d1d02c6d-b917-4848-99ce-8407b6f182c2",
      "metadata": {
        "id": "d1d02c6d-b917-4848-99ce-8407b6f182c2"
      },
      "outputs": [],
      "source": [
        "print(response.content)"
      ]
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "execution_count": null,
      "id": "746b60a2-eebb-4500-9738-3303298db442",
      "metadata": {
        "id": "746b60a2-eebb-4500-9738-3303298db442"
      },
      "outputs": [],
      "source": [
        "print(response.additional_kwargs['reasoning_content'])"
      ]
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "execution_count": null,
      "id": "27317610-5a03-42ba-9b3f-0b1a02da2521",
      "metadata": {
        "id": "27317610-5a03-42ba-9b3f-0b1a02da2521"
      },
      "outputs": [],
      "source": [
        "print(response)"
      ]
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "execution_count": null,
      "id": "ed4c760b-c1cb-411c-a505-dd907c66c117",
      "metadata": {
        "id": "ed4c760b-c1cb-411c-a505-dd907c66c117"
      },
      "outputs": [],
      "source": [
        "response.tool_calls"
      ]
    },

      },
      "source": [
        "## Structure the tool-invocation process"
      ]
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "execution_count": null,
      "id": "df376ba3-3dec-4144-b844-6cc0c0f55386",
      "metadata": {
        "id": "df376ba3-3dec-4144-b844-6cc0c0f55386"
      },
      "outputs": [],
      "source": [
        "def llm_with_tools(messages, tools):\n",
        "    response = model.invoke(messages)\n",
        "    tool_start=0\n",
        "    for tool_call in response.tool_calls:\n",
        "        tool_name = tool_call['name'].lower()\n",
        "        for tool in tools:\n",
        "            if tool.name == tool_name:\n",
        "                tool_output = tool.invoke(tool_call)\n",
        "                messages.append(tool_output)\n",
        "                tool_start=1\n",
        "\n",
        "    if tool_start==1:\n",
        "        tool_start=0\n",
        "        response = llm_with_tools(messages, tools)\n",
        "    return response"
      ]
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "execution_count": null,
      "id": "5fdbe9d2-bbeb-4e10-b1b3-a57dad0f3120",

      },
      "outputs": [],
      "source": [
        "messages = [HumanMessage(prompt)]"

      },
      "outputs": [],
      "source": [
        "import re\n",
        "\n",
        "def clean_text(text):\n",
        "    \"\"\"\n",
        "    Cleans the given text by:\n",
        "    - Removing extra whitespace (spaces, tabs, newlines)\n",
        "    - Stripping leading/trailing whitespace\n",
        "    - Removing unwanted control characters\n",
        "    \"\"\"\n",
        "    # Strip leading and trailing whitespace\n",
        "    cleaned = text.strip()\n",
        "    # Replace newlines, tabs, and multiple spaces with a single space\n",
        "    cleaned = re.sub(r\"\\s+\", \" \", cleaned)\n",
        "    # Optionally remove non-printable/control characters except basic punctuation\n",
        "    cleaned = re.sub(r\"[^\\x20-\\x7E]\", \"\", cleaned)\n",
        "    return cleaned"
      ]
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "execution_count": null,
      "id": "a519e971-3a0e-43b8-b3a1-bd46cfa85878",
      "metadata": {
        "id": "a519e971-3a0e-43b8-b3a1-bd46cfa85878"
      },
      "outputs": [],
      "source": [
        "response_content = clean_text(final_response.content)\n",
        "print(response_content)"
      ]
    },

      "outputs": [],
      "source": [
        "from langchain_core.prompts import ChatPromptTemplate, MessagesPlaceholder\n",
        "from langchain_core.messages import HumanMessage, AIMessage\n",
        "\n",
        "prompt_template = ChatPromptTemplate([\n",
        "    (\"system\", \"You are an Aircrash Investigator.\"),\n",
        "    MessagesPlaceholder(\"msgs\")\n",
        "])\n",
        "\n",
        "# More complex example with conversation history\n",
        "messages_to_pass = [\n",
        "    HumanMessage(content=query),\n",
        "    AIMessage(content=response_content),\n",
        "    HumanMessage(content=\"Provide a clear, detailed report summarizing the findings, probable causes, and recommendations for future safety improvements.\")\n",
        "]\n",
        "\n",
        "formatted_prompt = prompt_template.invoke({\"msgs\": messages_to_pass})\n",
        "print(formatted_prompt)"
      ]
    },

        "    verbose=True\n",
        ")"
